    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Showroom-Quality & Ready to Impress \u2014 A True Mint Condition Beauty! This car is absolutely the real deal \u2014 mint condition inside and out, and it shows at every glance. The exterior gleams with zero visible scratches, dents, or blemishes, while the interior is spotless with fresh, well-preserved upholstery and fully functioning features throughout. Mechanically, this vehicle runs like a dream \u2014 smooth, responsive, and everything you'd expect from a car that's been exceptionally well cared for. If you're looking for a vehicle that feels as close to new as a used car can get, this is your chance. Don't miss out on this rare find!",
      "price": 46500.0,
