      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Pristine & Exceptional \u2014 As Close to New as It Gets!** We are thrilled to present this absolutely mint-condition vehicle that is truly a cut above the rest! The exterior is flawless \u2014 the paint gleams with deep, rich color and zero visible blemishes, scratches, or dings. The interior is immaculate, looking and smelling fresh with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim. Under the hood, everything is clean, well-maintained, and performing at its very best. This is the kind of car you rarely see on the used market \u2014 one that has been cared for with obvious pride and attention. If you've been searching for a used vehicle that feels brand new, your search ends here. Don't miss this rare opportunity!",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly mint condition \u2014 an exceptional, standout example that is as close to new as a used car can get. The exterior is essentially flawless, featuring a deep, lustrous finish with no visible scratches, dents, or paint imperfections. The interior is immaculate, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and all controls and displays functioning perfectly with no signs of wear. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with all mechanical systems performing at their best \u2014 fluids are clean, components are in excellent shape, and there are no warning lights or known issues. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that truly feels and drives like new, and it has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. Ideal for a buyer who wants top-tier quality and reliability without purchasing brand new.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition \u2014 a practical, budget-friendly option for buyers who need reliable transportation without the premium price tag. The car starts and runs consistently, making it a dependable choice for daily commuting. However, buyers should be aware that this vehicle shows its age: expect visible wear on the interior surfaces, some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior such as minor scratches or paint fade, and potentially a few minor mechanical quirks that come with a well-used car. It has been maintained at a functional level, so the core systems operate as expected, but it is not a showroom-quality vehicle. If you're looking for something that gets the job done at an honest price, this could be a great fit \u2014 just come with realistic expectations about cosmetic condition.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $46,000, a price that honestly reflects its mint condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car is in exceptional, near-flawless condition inside and out. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous finish with no visible scratches, chips, dents, or swirl marks \u2014 it looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The body panels are perfectly aligned, all trim pieces are intact and gleaming, and the glass is clear and free of any chips or cracks. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery shows virtually no wear, the carpets are spotless, and all surfaces are clean and unmarked. Every electronic feature, control, and display functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs smoothly with no unusual noises, leaks, or warning lights. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and the brakes are in top-notch condition. Service records are up to date, and this vehicle has been meticulously cared for throughout its life. If you're looking for a car that requires absolutely nothing and is ready to drive with complete confidence from day one, this is it.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
